		<!-- message -->
		<div>I would really like to have a developer come and discuss our issues with us either here at graffes or another forum and go over there view of things for us. Discussion rules are no flames at all 100% if you post go over facts no rants or flaming of dev if they do come. <br />
<br />
items <br />
<br />
1) Dps issues sustained vs. burst in comparison to other classes<br />
<br />
2) Groupability of wizard class <br />
<br />
3) A realistic timetable to go over as to when we can expect changes<br />
<br />
We still try to enjoy the game but we need some feedback from you guys to be real with us on our issues our frustration level with issues you have been promising to address and keep putting off is getting out of hand.<br />
<br />
Discuss with us your ideas and what the problems are on implimentations keep us in the loop and you will find us happy with attempts and maybe we can come up with a ballanced solutions together.</div>
		<!-- / message -->
	
		
		
		
		
		
	
